---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import TeamCard from '../components/Team-Card.astro';
---

<Layout title="Mosbius Designs">
	<main>
		<div class="intro">
		<h1>Client Testimonials</h1>
		<p class="instructions">
			<p>At Mosbius Designs, we proudly stand by our work. However, you donâ€™t have to take our word for it; read through our client testimonials below and find out why our clients appreciate working with our firm.</p>
		</p></div>
		<div>
		<ul role="list" class="link-card-grid">
			<TeamCard
				title="Hammond Druthers"
				subtitle="Spokane Financial Institution"
				body="We wanted a modern bulding that still captured the distinct flavor and history of the northwest, and that is exactly what Mosbius Designs provided!"
			/>
			<TeamCard
				title="James Stinson"
				subtitle="Shaker Falls Community Library"
				body="When we were designing and building the building, Mr. Mosby was always willing to sit down to discuss the progress of the job and listen to our input. Since he and his family stem from Ohio."
			/>
			<TeamCard
				title="Marshall Eriksen"
				subtitle="Minnesota Lake Home"
				body="You have been nothing but top notch since the first time I met you.  You made Lily and I feel at ease about out upcoming project. If everything is looking good from Ted we don't plan on even contacting any other architects.  We are very pleased with how everything is going so far."
			/>
			<TeamCard
				title="Carl and Wendy"
				subtitle="Florida Retirement Home"
